### ðŸ  Home Screen

This folder contains additional CSS tweaks for the home screen layout.

To activate the icons for the home tab bar, paste the following code into **Dashboard â†’ General â†’ Branding â†’ Custom CSS**:
```css
/* Home Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-home::before {
    content: "home";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}
/* Favoriten Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-favorites::before {
    content: "favorite";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}
/* Watchlist Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-watchlist::before {
    content: "bookmark";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}
/* Bookmark+ Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-bookmarkadd::before {
    content: "bookmark_add";
    font-family: 'Material Symbols Rounded';
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}
```

> âš ï¸ **Important:** This code only works if your Jellyfin is set to **German language**!
> If you use a different language, the tab class names (e.g. `tab-home`, `tab-favorites`) will be different.
> You will need to **adjust the class names to match your language** â€” AI tools like Claude or ChatGPT can help you adapt the code to your language quickly!

Click **Save** and hard refresh your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R).

**Then apply the additional tweaks from this folder:**
1. Add the CSS from the `Home screen` folder below the code above
2. Click **Save** and hard refresh your browser again
